# SPARQL
# 1. What is the average price of games per company (AVG)
# 2. How many employees work on "Among Us" (COUNT)
# 3. What games were published between 2015-01-01 and 2019-01-01 per company
# 4. What is the name of the company that published the game "Among Us" which was developed by Gordon Ramsay, a game developer.
# 5. Which game has the largest size after 2018-01-01 (MAX)

# SHACL
# 1. A company should have a name with the format xsd:string
# 2. A game should only have one published date
# 3. A game has a minimum of 1 GB
# 4. A game can be played with a controller in this list: mouse, keyboard, gamepad
# 5. A company should have at least one game that is distributed in digital format